content:
How can you implement a hover effect on a tag that changes the background color to green and the text color to black? Also, what is the CSS code for centering the tag both horizontally and vertically on a webpage? 
[Formula for centering a tag horizontally: margin: 0 auto;
Formula for centering a tag vertically: display: flex;
                                 align-items: center;
                                 justify-content: center;]
Please provide the complete CSS code for achieving both effects.
